Same problem as Party-Angel, installs fine, says its registered but then on program open, it says trial is expired. -.-'

Those getting trial expired message. Set your folder options to show hidden folders, then go to program data and find the slysoft folder, then open the anydvd folder and delete the anydvd.chk file. After that all should be good for you. But please dont forget to uncheck the box regarding automatic updates.

go to C:\Documents and Settings\All Users\Application Data\SlySoft\AnyDVD and
delete the anydvd.chk file
then go back and run the key.anydvd file
run the program
